WEBVTT

00:02.569 --> 00:04.069
<i>In the last episode of</i> Soap,

00:04.070 --> 00:06.071
<i>much to Detective Donohue's</i>
<i>surprise,</i>

00:06.072 --> 00:08.073
<i>Jessica decided</i>
<i>to have an affair with him,</i>

00:08.074 --> 00:10.576
<i>and the next morning,</i>
<i>much to everyone's surprise,</i>

00:10.577 --> 00:12.578
<i>Chester returned home.</i>

00:12.579 --> 00:14.079
<i>Sally was surprised</i>

00:14.080 --> 00:15.581
<i>when Burt showed up</i>
<i>at her apartment</i>

00:15.582 --> 00:17.583
<i>to find out why she told</i>
<i>those surprising stories</i>

00:17.584 --> 00:19.084
<i>about him,</i>

00:19.085 --> 00:21.086
<i>and Burt was surprised</i>
<i>to find out</i>

00:21.087 --> 00:24.590
<i>it was because Ingrid Swenson</i>
<i>was blackmailing her.</i>

00:24.591 --> 00:27.092
<i>Corinne came home</i>
<i>with her beautiful healthy baby</i>

00:27.093 --> 00:28.594
<i>that she had</i>

00:28.595 --> 00:30.095
<i>after a surprisingly short</i>
<i>pregnancy.</i>

00:30.096 --> 00:32.097
<i>Tim hasn't been surprised</i>
<i>with the news yet,</i>

00:32.098 --> 00:33.599
<i>since he's now living in a cave.</i>

00:33.600 --> 00:35.100
<i>Surprised?</i>

00:35.101 --> 00:38.104
<i>You won't be after</i>
<i>tonight's episode of...</i> Soap.

00:43.109 --> 00:45.110
<i>This is the story</i>
<i>of two sisters,</i>

00:45.111 --> 00:47.613
<i>Jessica Tate</i>

00:47.614 --> 00:50.115
<i>and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:50.116 --> 00:53.619
<i>These are the Tates,</i>

00:53.620 --> 00:57.122
<i>and these are the Campbells.</i>

00:57.123 --> 00:59.125
<i>And this is</i> Soap.

